content: Madonna is one of the biggest business woman in the world. That concert was certainly sponsored. Alcohol and other types of beverages were flowing and not for free. The public got an incredible free experience with Madonna a worldwide icon. The sponsors got a physical market of customers of 1,6 millions in one night and all the media covers coming with. An audience to whom they advertised and sold their products and services. Of course the Madonna got a check behind doors. That is an entire MBA case study.
